name: thedailybeast
text: NEW: Trump’s attempt to overturn the results of the 2020 election has created a fissure within his own ranks, as top campaign officials and allied donors seek distance from a legal effort that they increasingly view as a pointless laughingstock. https://t.co/57k4oHjyHE

name: thedailybeast
text: Staff in campaign leadership roles have disappeared from public view. Others, including Bill Stepien, have had limited involvement in the legal campaign to challenge vote results, and have privately said they want nothing to do with it https://t.co/57k4oHjyHE

name: thedailybeast
text:
Trump and GOP mega-donor Shalabh “Shalli” Kumar is pulling out of the fight to overturn the results. 

“The president is entitled to whatever legal defense he wants to have... but I am not going to contribute any funds to that." https://t.co/57k4oHjyHE

name: thedailybeast
text: Even the Trump Make America Great Again Committee’s incessant “Election Defense Fund” fundraising emails have started hedging their language when it comes to allegations of widespread voter fraud. https://t.co/57k4oHjyHE
